- ğŸ“Š **Rich CLI Interface** - 8 powerful command groups for querying and analyzing data
- ğŸ“ˆ **Beautiful Graphs** - Professional NOC-style graphs with dark theme
- ğŸ“¤ **Data Export** - Export to CSV, JSON, or view as formatted tables
- ğŸ” **Smart Event Detection** - Debounced alerts for meaningful events only
- ğŸ·ï¸ **Network Profiles** - Rename, tag, and organize your networks
- ğŸ”„ **Network Comparison** - Compare performance across different ISPs
- ğŸ’¾ **SQLite Storage** - Lightweight, portable, no external database needed
- ğŸ–¥ï¸ **Cross-Platform** - Works on Linux, macOS, and Windows

